name: Aram Chouldjian Baghdassarian
about: Gosh, I feel like these always come off as so generic and cliche and have always wondered what I can do to make them seem less trite. Do people even read these? I'm genuinely curious, so if you're reading this then click http://bit.ly/yes-i-actually-read-the-bio. When you open the link, you'll find instructions to see how many people also clicked the link!
